init_text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the most important thing students should learn in school is how to learn.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that this is the most important thing because it will help them in their future.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If they can learn how to interact with other people, they will be able to get along with them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be able to get along with their friends and their family.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be able to get along with their teachers and their bosses.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be able to get along with their coworkers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be able to get along with their neighbors.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be able to get along with the people they meet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If we don't, we will have a hard life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that the most important thing I have learned in school is how to communicate with other people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She taught us how to listen to each other, and how to speak in a way that would be heard.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She taught us how to be respectful of each other, and how to be honest with each other.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She taught us how to be empathetic towards each other, and how to be kind to each other.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She taught us how to be good friends, and how to be good family members.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: How has this knowledge affected my life?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It has made my life much better.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have learned how to communicate with other people, and I have learned how to listen to them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I avoided many fights by listening to what the other person was saying, and trying to understand their point of view.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have a good job, and I have a good life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have good friends, and I have a good family.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have a good life, and I owe it to my ability to communicate with other people.
